org.apache.jackrabbit.oak.spi.gc

Class LoggingGCMonitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.jackrabbit.oak.spi.gc.LoggingGCMonitor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GCMonitor

    public class LoggingGCMonitor
extends java.lang.Object
implements GCMonitor
    This GCMonitor implementation logs all calls to its info(String, Object...), warn(String, Object...), error(String, Exception) and skipped(String, Object...) methods at the respective levels using the logger instance passed to the constructor.
